description: In order to use tracking and return features, you must first link your account on the Alexa app by submitting your email used to order items online. We will proceed to send you an email with a link that you can click to verify your identity. From there, you can ask questions about any open orders ("Where is my laptop backpack?") or about returning your items ("Can I return an item?").
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask e. bags where is my order?
Alexa, ask e. bags where is my laptop backpack?
Alexa, tell e. bags I want to return an item.
name: eBags
shortDescription: Always be up to date on the status of your orders from online shopping. You can also return your items and get a shipping label.
